start water

title "Water molecule energy calculation"

geometry units angstroms print xyz autosym
  O       -0.50200        0.37200        0.00000
  H        0.54700       -0.77600        0.59100
  H       -1.62300        1.56200       -0.60000
end

basis
  * library 6-31g
end

scf
  maxiter 200
end

dft
  xc b3lyp
  iterations 200
  convergence energy 1.0e-6
end

task dft energy
